<p><span>开</span><span>园当天</span><span>，来</span><span>自教育</span><span>、医护、交通、社</span><span>区</span><span>、法院、消防、公</span><span>安</span><span>、供</span><span>水</span><span>等行</span><span>业的</span><span>青年</span><span>人</span><span>在</span><span>现场发出</span><span>合肥</span><span>人的</span><span>“青年</span><span>宣言</span><span>”，表达</span><span>了乘风破浪</span><span>、奋斗</span><span>当下</span><span>、青春</span><span>无悔的</span><span>新</span><span>时代青年心声</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201001/bfc3abd9b48b4b76992a741960c852d6.png" /></p>
<p><span>新</span><span>时代青年心声。</span></p>
<p><span>除</span><span>此以外</span><span>，青年</span><span>人的活力</span><span>也</span><span>感染着</span><span>前</span><span>来的市民</span><span>。上</span><span>午</span><span>1</span><span>0</span><span>：30，记</span><span>者到达</span><span>现场</span><span>时</span><span>，现场</span><span>已经人潮涌动</span><span>，“安子与九妹”乐</span><span>队的歌声和</span><span>青年</span><span>人的欢</span><span>呼</span><span>让你</span><span>的</span><span>情绪轻易就被</span><span>“带</span><span>了</span><span>节奏”。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201001/e4b635dfa702491185f8732c43c5ed2f.png" /></p>
<p><span>安</span><span>子与九妹乐队开唱。</span></p>
<p><span>“1号</span><span>和</span><span>2号，我们</span><span>邀请了</span><span>安子与九妹、棱镜乐队、阁楼乐队、潮池蓝、摩登乐队、李伟与DL乐团，与</span><span>大家共度国庆</span><span>。”</span><span>主办方</span><span>合肥</span><span>东部新中心文化旅游公司负责人许</span><span>琦</span><span>介绍</span><span>，此</span><span>次合肥东部新中心青年田园项</span><span>目</span><span>开园</span><span>，特意设置的</span><span>文创大赛、潮玩音乐节、先锋影像展</span><span>、文创市集、星空露营等五大独具“青春、创意”特色的线上线下活动</span><span>已经全</span><span>面</span><span>启</span><span>动</span><span>，市</span><span>民</span><span>均</span><span>可以积极参与进来</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201001/f3546f298e4c423f882bf4a3df561c81.png" /></p>
<p><span>国</span><span>庆主题景观。</span></p>
<p><span>记</span><span>者进一步了解到</span><span>，青年</span><span>创意田园作为</span><span>合肥</span><span>市全力建设的合肥东部新中心最新</span><span>落</span><span>成开放项目</span><span>，是</span><span>合肥东部新中心第一个生态文化项目</span><span>。以“华</span><span>东</span><span>青年</span><span>中心</span><span>、安徽</span><span>双创中心</span><span>、合肥</span><span>东部</span><span>中</span><span>心</span><span>”为</span><span>三大定位的合肥东部新中心</span><span>，目前</span><span>城市基础设施</span><span>、配套</span><span>设施建设不</span><span>断</span><span>提速</span><span>，合肥</span><span>市</span><span>妇</span><span>女</span><span>儿</span><span>童中心</span><span>、合肥</span><span>工业博物馆</span><span>以</span><span>及一批</span><span>重大</span><span>教育项目</span><span>都</span><span>在快速推进中</span><span>，多</span><span>家央企</span><span>将</span><span>参与到合肥东部新中心建设</span><span>中</span><span>来</span><span>。（刘</span><span>华</span><span>）</span></p>
